    {
      "parameters": {
        "language": "python",
        "pythonCode": "from datetime import datetime\nimport random\n\nnow = datetime.now()\ndate_str = now.strftime(\"%m/%d/%Y\")\ntime_str = now.strftime(\"%H:%M\")\n\n# Characters to randomly reference for flavor\ncharacter = random.choice([\n    \"Cheerful Girl in Pink\",\n    \"Tiny Mermaid Girl\",\n    \"Adorable Elf Girl\",\n    \"Joyful Princess\",\n    \"Cute Wizard Girl\",\n    \"Playful School Girl\"\n])\n\n# URLs\nYoutube_Channel_Url = \"https://youtube.com/@algonovalabs?si=p6UJAPdolW5Mfdq5\"\nYoutube_Channel_name = \"AlgoNova Labs\"\nYoutube_Video_Url = f\"https://www.youtube.com/shorts/{_('Get many videos').first().json.id.videoId}\"\n\nprompt = f\"\"\"\nIMPORTANT:\nUse the exact YouTube video and channel URLs below for posts,\nbut NOT for YouTube comments (those are posted directly on that same video).\n\nVideo URL:\n{Youtube_Video_Url}\n\nChannel URL:\n{Youtube_Channel_Url}\n\nTASK:\nFor each platform below, generate 5 completely unique and creative variations. \nDo NOT reuse fixed templates — invent new phrases every time while maintaining the tone.\n• Facebook  \n• Instagram  \n• X (Twitter) — under 280 characters, must include both links  \n• YouTube Community — must include both the video + channel links  \n• YouTube Comment — should feel like the AlgoNova world calling the viewer to *enter*, purely dynamic and whimsical, no links, no hashtags\n\nTONE:\n- Whimsical ✨ Dreamlike 🌙 Playfully Mysterious 🍭  \n- Sound like a living fairytale inviting people in — “step through,” “come closer,” “follow the light,” etc.  \n- Encourage interaction (“What would you bring if you visited?” / “Which door would you open first?”).  \n- Lightly FOMO-driven: tease the beauty or emotion inside the short without spoiling it.  \n- Feel personal, curious, alive — *never corporate*.\n\nRULES:\n1. Include BOTH URLs exactly as provided (except YouTube comments).  \n2. YouTube Comment: NO URLs, NO hashtags — just pure engagement.  \n3. Each variation must be unique; words, sentence structures, and metaphors should differ.  \n4. Use emojis and vivid, sensory language.  \n5. Output ONLY valid JSON.\n\nOUTPUT FORMAT (STRICT):\nReturn ONLY valid JSON using this structure (use the FIRST variation per platform as default):\n\n{{\n  \"Date\": \"{date_str}\",\n  \"Time\": \"{time_str}\",\n  \"Facebook Post\": \"FIRST CREATIVE VARIATION HERE\",\n  \"Instagram Post\": \"FIRST CREATIVE VARIATION HERE\",\n  \"X Post\": \"FIRST CREATIVE VARIATION HERE (must include both links, <280 chars)\",\n  \"Youtube Post\": \"FIRST CREATIVE VARIATION HERE. Watch till the end! {Youtube_Channel_name}: {Youtube_Channel_Url}\",\n  \"Youtube Comment\": \"FIRST DYNAMIC WHIMSICAL COMMENT GENERATED BY AI\",\n  \"Status\": \"Ready to Post\",\n  \"Category\": \"Community Engagement\",\n  \"Notes\": \"Each variation must feel freshly invented — whimsical, engaging, and alive. Let the AI explore endless magical phrasing, metaphors, and curiosity triggers.\"\n}}\n\"\"\"\n\nreturn {'chatInput': prompt}\n"
      },
